    dc:creator "Karaouzas, Ioannis; Waringer, Johann" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "The larva of Polycentropus ierapetra Malicky 1972 (Trichoptera: Polycentropodidae), including a key to the larvae of genus Polycentropus (Curtis 1835) in the Hellenic western Balkan region" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.833863>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.833859>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.833857>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.833861> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.833863>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 9. Polycentropodidae genn. spp., 5 th instar larvae. 8, Neureclipsis bimaculata (Linnaeus 1758), tip of abdomen, ventral. 9, Cyrnus trimaculatus (Curtis 1834), left anal claw, left lateral. a = basal segment of anal proleg; b = spines; c = anal claw teeth. Scale bar Fig. 8 = 1 mm; scale bar Fig. 9 = 0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/833863/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.833859>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 4. Polycentropus ierapetra Malicky 1972, 5 th instar larva. 3, head and thoracic legs, ventral. 4, anal prolegs and claws, left lateral. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/833859/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.833857>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 2. Polycentropus ierapetra Malicky 1972, 5 th instar larva. 1, head and pronotum, dorsal. 2, head and pronotum, right lateral. d = projected length of longitudinal axis of muscle attachment spot ‘ m’; m = muscle attachment spot ‘ m’. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/833857/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.833861>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 7. Polycentropus spp., 5 th instar larvae. 5, Polycentropus excisus Klapálek 1894, head, dorsal. 6 – 7, Polycentropus flavomaculatus (Pictet 1834), 5 th instar larva: 6, head, dorsal; 7, left anal claw, left lateral. d = projected length of longitudinal axis of muscle attachment spot ‘ m’; m = muscle attachment spot ‘ m’. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/833861/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

